Tight integration for openmpi was tested with version
openmpi-1.4.5 as well as openmpi-1.6.0.

Building openmpi
================
When you build openmpi, make sure to configure with option --with-sge.

Installing the PE
=================
qconf -Ap $SGE_ROOT/mpi/openmpi/openmpi.template

==> special option to mpirun to extend the number of qrsh -inherit!
